<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">求除数是37的商法，一个四位数除以37时，如果这个四位数中间的两个数字相同，且等于首末两位数字的和，可将首末两位数字合成一个两位数，然后再乘以3，其积就是要求的商。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">4773÷37=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 4773÷37</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=43×3</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=129</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>